            <!-- BEGIN: customer-engagement-fabric-TopBanner -->
            <div class="common-banner col-top-banner" data-config="{'backgroundColor':'#e3f4ff', 'backgroundImage':'//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/production/customer-engagement-fabric_banner.png','imageHeight':'auto'}">
                <div class="common-banner-image">
                    <div class="common-banner-title">
                        <img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/production/customer-engagement-fabric_icon.svg" />
                        <h2>Customer Engagement Fabric <span style="color: #4d4d4d;font-family: '微软雅黑',regular;font-size: 20px;top: -6px;position: relative;display: inline;">(Preview)</span><span>Customer Engagement Fabric</span></h2>
                        <h4>Provide unified API and SDK to accelerate development of customer engagement functions including notification, authentication, and payment. Improve operational efficiency through increased development efficiency and unified management of user data.</h4>
                        <em><a href="/pricing/1rmb-trial/" id="customer-engagement-fabric_1rmb-trial">Apply for 1RMB Trial<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></em> <a href="/pricing/pia/" id="customer-engagement-fabric_pia">Buy Now<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- END: customer-engagement-fabric-TopBanner --> <!-- BEGIN: customer-engagement-fabric-Content -->
            <div class="pricing-page-section">
                <p>Customer Engagement Fabric (CEF) brings together many service providers to enable a series of services that allow personalized customer engagement between businesses and customers using apps. This includes multi-channel notification services, sign-in verification, and aggregate functions for payment. These services can help the app to quickly implement relevant user connectivity functions, improve user engagement, and analyze user behavior data to improve the operational efficiency of the app.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pricing-page-section">
                <h2>Notification service</h2>
                <p>Provide robust and efficient text messaging notification, email notification, and app push services with high availability rate and intelligent One Notification.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pricing-page-section">
                <h2>Sign-in verification</h2>
                <p>Provide simplified API to implement social login and One-Time-Password verification to accelerate development of customer engagement functions and quickly onboard users.
</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pricing-page-section">
                <h2>Aggregate functions for payment</h2>
                <p>Provide unified API to accelerate implementation of third-party payment functions, unified management of payment data, and analysis of user behavior data.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pricing-page-section">
				<h2>List of subservices (in Public Preview)</h2>
				<div class="message-box col-md-6">
					<h3>Text messaging service</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Supports notification reminder, text messaging verification code, and marketing text messaging</li>
						<li>arrival within 5 seconds, 99% arrival rate</li>
						<li>Trip-Play, 10690 dedicated channels</li>
						<li>Fast API access, real-time data statistics</li>
					</ul>
					<p><a href="/home/features/customer-engagement-fabric/sms/">Find out more</a></p>
				</div>
                <div class="third-part col-md-6">
					<h3>Social Login</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Unified SDK, allow accelerated third-party social login integration</li>
						<li>Reduce development time</li>
						<li>Quickly onboard users</li>
						<li>Aggregates data to make statistical analysis easier</li>
					</ul>
					<p><a href="/home/features/customer-engagement-fabric/social-login/">Find out more</a></p>
				</div>
